716
00:55:44,299 --> 00:55:47,969
Pergi!

717
00:55:48,053 --> 00:55:49,387
Baiklah, semua!

718
00:55:49,471 --> 00:55:53,183
Biar mereka dengar jeritan kita, kemarahan kita!

719
